  "text": "As the Magnox reactors approached their design lives, it became apparent that the dosimetry related materials issues were more diverse and challenging than had been originally anticipated. In the late 1980's a ten year programme of measurements, methods developments and dosimetry assessments was begun to support continued operation of the Magnox plant [CITATION_1] . Some issues affecting Magnox were shown to be relevant and prompted developments to the AGR dosimetry programme.",
